review_text: Ashton is not the cheapest company around but you pay for the quality. They tried hard to find out the issue of our water pressure and lukewarm water. Was not a quick or simple fix but we have hot water now.
response_from_owner_text: Hi Oliver, thank you for taking the time to leave us a review. Were so glad we were able to resolve your hot water issue in your building. Thank you for choosing Ashton.
Thank you for leaving us a 5 star rating!
